Topic: Your AI articles read fine but say nothing new.

Summary: This post introduces the Fan-Out Framework, a strategy for improving visibility in both traditional search engines and AI-powered search. Unlike traditional SEO, AI search generates answers from multiple sources, making it important for brands to appear across related topics and connected queries rather than just ranking for one keyword. The framework encourages creating comprehensive, interconnected content that covers a topic from multiple angles. This increases the chances of being referenced by AI search engines and appearing in AI-generated responses.
Key Takeaways:

Takeaway 1 AI search rewards topic coverage
Takeaway 2 Visibility across multiple sources matters
Takeaway 3 SEO is evolving


